form_in_progress.dset_network_configuration: If this dataset includes data captured from a network, describe that network and its configuration.
form_in_progress.dset_nontech_description: A brief overview of this dataset: what kind of data is included, how and when was it captured? Save the technical details about each trace, and each traceset, for the pages describing the respective trace(s) and traceset(s).
form_in_progress.dset_sanitization: It is the responsibility of you (the contributor) to ensure your dataset is properly “sanitized” before transfer to CRAWDAD. Sanitization includes the removal or modification of sensitive data about humans or organizations. If your data includes any information about human individuals - whether identifiable or not - it must be anonymized before upload. Similarly, if the data includes any proprietary or other sensitive information, it should be redacted or obscured before upload. Provide details of sanitization methods in description of each traceset.
form_in_progress.tset1_tech_description: Please use this box to describe the technical details of this particular traceset. All traces within a traceset share a common collection method, sanitization method, and file format. Details specific to the trace(s) within this traceset should be entered on subsequent page(s) in which those traces are described.
